  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Vulkan-Loader</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Vulkan-Loader</application> package contains a library
      which provides the Vulkan API and provides core support for graphics
      drivers for Vulkan.
    </para>

    &lfs123_checked;

